text: Regina Daniels (born October 10, 2000) is a Nigerian actress and a film producer. she is a business woman and a Serial Entrepreneur. ==Early life and education== Regina Daniels was born on the 10th of October 2000, in Lagos Nigeria. She is a Nollywood film actress and a model. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian actors
